{"tid":437032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好想要個家？","createTime":"2017-10-15T15:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T16:35:40.000Z","uid":39046,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb3f7e11588fa478e675d62ef2384fb4b37bb4a","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"呀爸有第二個家<br />\n本身同2兄妹住 但佢地都有男女朋友<br />\n唔會番屋企訓。<br />\n每晚訓得自己一個 每朝醒得自己一個<br />\n番完學 番到屋企又係自己一個<br />\n唔會有人照顧 無人煮飯<br />\n餐餐食外賣<br />\n成個心都好空盪盪 好想要歸屬。<br />\n今日打8號波 岩岩想叫個外賣都無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645022426cad492fcee597a4efbc0a5a2547b04b","tid":437032,"uid":15389,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀爸有第二個家<br />\n本身同2兄妹住 但佢地都有男女朋友<br />\n唔會番屋企訓。<br />\n每晚訓得自己一個 每朝醒得自己一個<br />\n番完學 番到屋企又係自己一個<br />\n唔會有人照顧 無人煮飯<br />\n餐餐食外賣<br />\n成個心都好空盪盪 好想要歸屬。<br />\n今日打8號波 岩岩想叫個外賣都無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學識自己照顧自己<br />\n慢慢你會由想煮個麵算數<br />\n變到想煮個意粉<br />\n再變到煮下飯<br />\n<br />\n以前啲野亂咁擺就算<br />\n慢慢就想執下佢<br />\n又慢慢想買啲盒呀櫃筒仔呀返嚟整理好佢<br />\n<br />\n慢慢你就越來越慣一個人了"},{"pid":"dd74b6a698221972b7e7ab6444c2806c7a09340d","tid":437032,"uid":150140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"巴打加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c73ebdbb268b04e711d3eea00e2677e742e487c","tid":437032,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"搵個男友囉"},{"pid":"2f4e11a3274e3ef21510c43026e0ea44cd8cf9f9","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呀爸有第二個家<br />\n本身同2兄妹住 但佢地都有男女朋友<br />\n唔會番屋企訓。<br />\n每晚訓得自己一個 每朝醒得自己一個<br />\n番完學 番到屋企又係自己一個<br />\n唔會有人照顧 無人煮飯<br />\n餐餐食外賣<br />\n成個心都好空盪盪 好想要歸屬。<br />\n今日打8號波 岩岩想叫個外賣都無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學識自己照顧自己<br />\n慢慢你會由想煮個麵算數<br />\n變到想煮個意粉<br />\n再變到煮下飯<br />\n<br />\n以前啲野亂咁擺就算<br />\n慢慢就想執下佢<br />\n又慢慢想買啲盒呀櫃筒仔呀返嚟整理好佢<br />\n<br />\n慢慢你就越來越慣一個人了</blockquote><br />\n反而我係由堅持煮飯<br />\n變左煮麵 再到叫外賣<br />\n一個人煮飯 好難買餸 好難預份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實比起當初 係習慣左一個人多d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f251820c63a0ed322beb2f78794454f1a6baebb","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93c517d9988ec162ed2a45fb1c1766f0a956223","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:50:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c31bbfc4f98d13a8bac7df92b001eac2908bcf","tid":437032,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391c96a155e61667d00756eaf0c40294c1b62c36","tid":437032,"uid":61436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"我暫時一個人住，我覺得幾好喎，可能我同左屋企人住左廿幾年，感覺唔同"},{"pid":"aa5351073c84c8d5f84289bf24a77c75d52800c4","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都算多朋友<br />\n但我覺得佢地比唔到想要既野我<br />\n我同佢地出街 都會開心<br />\n但一番到屋企 都係空盪盪"},{"pid":"bce41d52aa1164f05abee459748d7ddc0d8f8f69","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我暫時一個人住，我覺得幾好喎，可能我同左屋企人住左廿幾年，感覺唔同</blockquote><br />\n選擇一個人住 同被迫一個人住係唔同架<br />\n況且 你仲有個屋企你可以隨時番去"},{"pid":"4c37cd68db78733b3fbf94489bb5282a7ab01332","tid":437032,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"其實你想揾個另一半陪姐"},{"pid":"5ed683d163569f9bd9edbae10934010b64d06d55","tid":437032,"uid":148013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都算多朋友<br />\n但我覺得佢地比唔到想要既野我<br />\n我同佢地出街 都會開心<br />\n但一番到屋企 都係空盪盪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱鬧過後嘅失落 有個對比係到 其實個反差仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7652f31214364e3eaebd75f47c95e224bf44e5","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你想揾個另一半陪姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係想有歸屬感<br />\n有人在乎 在意 我唔想自己一個人住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2979504c31ed7c7c1c8c4569228bfdae2c2132a9","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都算多朋友<br />\n但我覺得佢地比唔到想要既野我<br />\n我同佢地出街 都會開心<br />\n但一番到屋企 都係空盪盪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱鬧過後嘅失落 有個對比係到 其實個反差仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀就係咁...."},{"pid":"e92bc891ece3f4bfd245a8aa83502c0ed9f2e5d9","tid":437032,"uid":112393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"長時間自己住應該要學下煮飯整餸<br />\n當為咗將來可以加分都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw巴打加油"},{"pid":"f9678f95c987ca109810b85e4ef04050cf11b63d","tid":437032,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都算多朋友<br />\n但我覺得佢地比唔到想要既野我<br />\n我同佢地出街 都會開心<br />\n但一番到屋企 都係空盪盪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱鬧過後嘅失落 有個對比係到 其實個反差仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀就係咁....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你起碼有朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9752d7f1428b3999cacabfa4279d19a81abb8e1","tid":437032,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你想揾個另一半陪姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係想有歸屬感<br />\n有人在乎 在意 我唔想自己一個人住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算你有兄弟姐妹 同朋友，到左大時大節佢都唔會陪到你架啦。你想人在乎，都係想要另一半姐。"},{"pid":"2a8ace350dc07d16cbd15a7eec72e573a463aae3","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長時間自己住應該要學下煮飯整餸<br />\n當為咗將來可以加分都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw巴打加油</blockquote><br />\n煮比自己食 真係好無動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想煮比人食就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw你都一樣情況？"},{"pid":"a0b4052faa6340a0e3bf51300ec8481cd8ecbea0","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d9c7lcnDfE&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=05af001d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d9c7lcnDfE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左佢 你會明我想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都算多朋友<br />\n但我覺得佢地比唔到想要既野我<br />\n我同佢地出街 都會開心<br />\n但一番到屋企 都係空盪盪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱鬧過後嘅失落 有個對比係到 其實個反差仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀就係咁....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你起碼有朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9664057efd5a003459aee8766c607461662eacb","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想揾個另一半陪姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係想有歸屬感<br />\n有人在乎 在意 我唔想自己一個人住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算你有兄弟姐妹 同朋友，到左大時大節佢都唔會陪到你架啦。你想人在乎，都係想要另一半姐。</blockquote><br />\n我想番到屋企有人可以傾下計<br />\n講真 我都想要個可以心靈溝通到既另一半"},{"pid":"b5c1a975b875a2e9c00ff7c43825c702e783f46b","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f206de069a5cb095d969c673b7330993025d77","tid":437032,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"日台中都有後生仔合租屋<br />\n香港劏到啲房咁撚樣 想識個roommate都難"},{"pid":"a1c5cf4efe92ce9160abcbbb61fb778e9c0d0b98","tid":437032,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"Call g la"},{"pid":"c80783f4eccd0185c537a94338b19c43c354e944","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日台中都有後生仔合租屋<br />\n香港劏到啲房咁撚樣 想識個roommate都難</blockquote><br />\n個環境仲要係差果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我宜家仲讀緊書 邊有錢租屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36771d9df07b693ed59fd973533789ba7eccb400","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Call g la</blockquote><br />\n我絲打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2616bc419f2cbd1907178211c09626f824c0f836","tid":437032,"uid":25840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Call g la</blockquote><br />\n我絲打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個人住先好 第時識到男友咪可以日日一齊住<br />\n得閒又可以叫人上來玩"},{"pid":"2f5b6d2fc39c71f22c68e10b0aec216df16e0e9b","tid":437032,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀爸有第二個家<br />\n本身同2兄妹住 但佢地都有男女朋友<br />\n唔會番屋企訓。<br />\n每晚訓得自己一個 每朝醒得自己一個<br />\n番完學 番到屋企又係自己一個<br />\n唔會有人照顧 無人煮飯<br />\n餐餐食外賣<br />\n成個心都好空盪盪 好想要歸屬。<br />\n今日打8號波 岩岩想叫個外賣都無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打風都叫外賣<br />\n唔怪得你無男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62920e595d35c6653373b1291b8e8db137593239","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呀爸有第二個家<br />\n本身同2兄妹住 但佢地都有男女朋友<br />\n唔會番屋企訓。<br />\n每晚訓得自己一個 每朝醒得自己一個<br />\n番完學 番到屋企又係自己一個<br />\n唔會有人照顧 無人煮飯<br />\n餐餐食外賣<br />\n成個心都好空盪盪 好想要歸屬。<br />\n今日打8號波 岩岩想叫個外賣都無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打風都叫外賣<br />\n唔怪得你無男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但夜晚都落左波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我落左波先想叫"},{"pid":"8ced3a9e756c44e5a1133ce19c8f5f5cf56b79ed","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Call g la</blockquote><br />\n我絲打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個人住先好 第時識到男友咪可以日日一齊住<br />\n得閒又可以叫人上來玩</blockquote><br />\n但宜家無呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebfee97bc5c14b54d5a9a841ee01f2dfb0e8b59","tid":437032,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"47535ce36a4d4d83d87e50700966906ad47603d0","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,