ote>搬黎同我住丫 好悶好凍呀呢到</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解你講到好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88c4d60abd5fd772aaf57bb07826e3fc7f08705","tid":437032,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:56:59.000Z","msg":"八號波咪撚叫外賣害鳩人啦"},{"pid":"c9eb5cad8c3960a28d1619fbd8c50da5f3e35e92","tid":437032,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:00:50.000Z","msg":"瞓啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28357e27b1b2058df1659740a9c32bd79d142a46","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八號波咪撚叫外賣害鳩人啦</blockquote><br />\n都話落左波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e202aecc0965c8d2f2aa1b5098a80b8ecc65fe","tid":437032,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:02:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d48e53c62ae836efc34fe2131e65da9ef844f59","tid":437032,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"唔敢講要個家<br />\n想有人聽下我講野就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9225f2b1a90a747aabedb07746f0b2cd6f526d1","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔敢講要個家<br />\n想有人聽下我講野就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁搵fd都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d8e1512364ecc23a3614839412c19e15ff7045","tid":437032,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔敢講要個家<br />\n想有人聽下我講野就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁搵fd都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵真心朋友唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bcf58c5c91967e76ba475fa9347c52f51c6be4","tid":437032,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:08:56.000Z","msg":"我都破碎家庭出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企雖然好多人住<br />\n但個感覺從來都同自己住無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企只係為左沖涼訓教<br />\n<br />\n自己同朋友係出面租左個地方玩<br />\n成日會約朋友上去玩, 仲養左隻兔係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係家既感覺<br />\n但感覺唔差"},{"pid":"0b38eeb8f92d81204559d64698294a4d43b0cfc3","tid":437032,"uid":13184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:10:39.000Z","msg":"搵我囉"},{"pid":"16c4fadce200961a7e4c8f0564ed1342280f28ea","tid":437032,"uid":3094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:19:51.000Z","msg":"我都係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a060d7882cc891aed5edf0f05f4f460a21670584","tid":437032,"uid":126102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"我形式上係有一個家 <br />\n但我覺得好壓抑 <br />\n佢地唔明白我 我都講到攰 唔想再解釋<br />\n好想搬走但又無能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570d2d28455f9a63ca5dac2925bf296ac8204e4d","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔敢講要個家<br />\n想有人聽下我講野就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁搵fd都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵真心朋友唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得難搵既 係有個岩傾既真心朋友"},{"pid":"803c3a977bcc7040bbfe349ab8497fb1fe73fd59","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都破碎家庭出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企雖然好多人住<br />\n但個感覺從來都同自己住無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返屋企只係為左沖涼訓教<br />\n<br />\n自己同朋友係出面租左個地方玩<br />\n成日會約朋友上去玩, 仲養左隻兔係上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係家既感覺<br />\n但感覺唔差</blockquote><br />\n你同班朋友感情好好呀嗚"},{"pid":"5c63ee59b15465f7d75a3aa70d28a295b8a74a21","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後呢 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33349f937eccc09b0bf1257679d0d1fdc00e46f1","tid":437032,"uid":146968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"我去陪你住？"},{"pid":"1877579a1fbdacb3394c44f18dca8bc8b12602a2","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我形式上係有一個家 <br />\n但我覺得好壓抑 <br />\n佢地唔明白我 我都講到攰 唔想再解釋<br />\n好想搬走但又無能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係屋企無人明好慘 唔會想再溝通<br />\n無能力只好被迫依賴佢地 無力感。<br />\n如果可以 我都想同人/朋友夾租 想搬出住"},{"pid":"f2ee536c307d14e8ccaee793e729a1d4c07e79a7","tid":437032,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"曾經好憧憬同第時同另一半建立一個溫暖嘅家<br />\n依家大咗, 對呢樣嘢開始冇乜期待, 自己一個都好可以好開心<br />\n反而想自己一個搬出嚟住多"},{"pid":"b0882a9f1dd02989c2ea818e97fb6ad7bb89aa9b","tid":437032,"uid":40029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"加油呀爸打，將來你一定會搵到個好老婆 一家三口齊齊整整"},{"pid":"7a85c6020ab6713ba0401005e827a1f42d1e4e51","tid":437032,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經好憧憬同第時同另一半建立一個溫暖嘅家<br />\n依家大咗, 對呢樣嘢開始冇乜期待, 自己一個都好可以好開心<br />\n反而想自己一個搬出嚟住多</blockquote><br />\n巴/絲打宜家幾歲？<br />\n唔知係咪我仲細 仲係好憧憬<img s